        <p><strong>Sec. 1.</strong> The Secretary of War&hellip; to prescribe military areas&hellip; from which any or all persons may be excluded, and with respect to which, the right of any person to enter, remain in, or leave shall be subject to whatever restriction the Secretary of War or the appropriate Military Commander may impose in his discretion.</p>
