        <div style="font-family:'Crimson Pro',serif;font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--pd);margin-bottom:0.45rem;font-style:italic;">The photograph was taken by the WRA Photography Division. The caption was written by the WRA Photography Division. What does it mean when the institution that carried out a policy also captions its own photographic record of that policy?</div>
